Territory of Washington County of King I do herby return to the Honorable J. R. Lewis Cheif Justice of the supreme court and judge of the 3rd judicial district court May before the coming to me of the written writ the said William Fox was committed to my custody and is detained by virtue of and then a written copy of which is such of which I also herewith produce newness I have the body of the said William Fox before you at the time day and place within mentioned as our nothing committed
June 14 1878 L. V. Wyckoff Sheriff
